CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 14, 2013

[Cite as 11/14/2013 Case Announcements #2, 2013-Ohio-5039.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1768. Chiro v. Foley.

Cuyahoga App. No. 99888, 2013-Ohio-4808. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

It is ordered by the court, sua sponte, that appellee shall file a response to appellant’s motion for stay of execution no later than 12:00 p.m. on Monday, November 18, 2013.
